## The run-on-import entry {Tangle}[index.ts]

This thin entry starts the server the moment it loads. The VS Code extension bundles it as `server.js`, and the `loom-language-server` bin runs it â€” both expect loading the module to start the server.

=>

import { startLanguageServer } from './LoomServer'

startLanguageServer()
